    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.abs(v1 + 0.32)) * (wp.abs(v2 + 0.65) - (tmp + 0.05 / v0 + 0.21)))
    v1 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.46 / v1 + 0.31)) / wp.exp((v1 + 0.07 + v0 + 0.75)))
    v0 = ((0.90 / (tmp + 0.85 * v2 + 0.82)) * wp.cos(tmp))
